Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.07,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}光る眼で闇を読む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:08.70,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}恐るべき子供達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:21.02,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}生まれてきた時からずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:26.92,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}愛とは凶器で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:34.76,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}真っ赤に濡れた胸を掴んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.29,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}傷口に埋めた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:44.96,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}腐敗の中から成せる世界には
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.66,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}華やぐ絶望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:51.67,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}生かすも殺すもわたしたちの業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.74,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}犬のように笑い　豚のように泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.34,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}喚きつづけたあとには
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.36,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}さあどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.65,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}守られあやされ毀れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.91,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}息づくこの身は抜け殻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:11.32,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ひび割れ煌めく心の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.62,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}引き金に指を掛け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.82,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}守られあやされ壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.22,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}すべてわかったふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.47,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}撃つのは甲斐なき幻ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.47,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\fs16\pos(484,449)}ゆめ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.07,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}闪光的眼瞳看透黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:08.70,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}令人畏惧的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:21.02,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}自出生时便一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:26.92,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}爱即为凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:34.76,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}紧抠已然沾满鲜红的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.29,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}将爱埋没于伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:44.96,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}由腐败中诞生的世界所拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.66,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}是繁华的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:51.67,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}放生抑或杀生都是我们的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.74,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}如猪狗一般发笑 流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.34,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}无病呻吟的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.36,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}还剩下什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.65,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在保护与诓骗中腐坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.91,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}虽生却犹如行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:11.32,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}耀眼的心灵出现裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.62,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}轻轻扣上心灵的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.82,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在保护与诓骗中毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.22,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}装作一切都了然于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.47,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}追逐的却尽是缥缈的梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:55.56,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}我们是没有容身之处的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:59.00,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}凭空于世的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:05.83,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}心失くしたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:17.44,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}ただ想い出すのが怖いような気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.97,ED_jap3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}忘れかけてた温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:35.65,ED_jap3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}掴もうとした手をすり抜けた幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:43.16,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}押し潰されそうになりながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:53.00,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}もう一度新しい明日を見たいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:59.62,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:02.12,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:08.84,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.96,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:18.34,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}透明になってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:05.84,ED_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}并非丢失了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:17.45,ED_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}只是对过去的记忆心存恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:24.98,ED_cht3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}游走在忘却边缘的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:35.66,ED_cht3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}那是渴望拥有却无法握紧的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:43.17,ED_cht1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}即使濒临崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:53.01,ED_cht1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}也想再次一睹崭新明天的风采
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:18.34,ED_cht4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}一切都渐渐透明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还…活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔·迪本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了…亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓要保护她 说好要回去找她的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 却让她孤单一人以至遭人毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事实并非如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的狙击…是她干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔她…作为狙击手生活在「Inferno」里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄老师 在您的寿诞这一值得纪念的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与您结下兄弟之义 实乃我徐建法一生的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徐 别这么谦虚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在日本西部建立了自己的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是对你的功绩给予一道迟来的表彰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的将来 关东地区也将纳入我们囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可靠啊 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们的前途干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉与梧桐组对立的中国黑手党大头目·徐 这就是委托内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要连黄老爷子也一并当成目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人可是在为与「Inferno」对立的组织撑腰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被赶出「Inferno」的时候 黄似乎照顾过你不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讲江湖道义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贯彻你的江湖道义就好 我可不一样 就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是格雷高 请指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷高队就位 随时可以行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先待机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Phantom」她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本来就无心参与这次行动 那就把她排除在外好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 只负责后援或许不适合她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷高 作战行动按原计划实行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先让帕卡队从后门进入 解决掉那些保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭他们把黄和徐逼出来 要花上3分钟吧？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 哪敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她出手的话只要10秒就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你在搞什么飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是最有效最合理的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是日本 你把事情搞这么大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人命的份量 无论日本还是美国都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 黄老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大胆的袭击到底是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是有点头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是塞斯的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助过那个男人的不是别人 正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他要恩将仇报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？ 什么意思来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有骨气的嘛 还抱有取胜之心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中意你 就陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢玩游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子放完之后就开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是哪个组织的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了这种事 别以为就能一走了之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Phantom」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是道上之人的话 至少听过这个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那说的就是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是赢了我的话 全世界的人一定都会向你膜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次投胎时 可别再入错行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}再见了 中国人{\r}\NAd{\fsp-4}iós{\r}   Chinese
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我制造的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我教了她杀人方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我带她踏进黑道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我亲手…把她的人生弄得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡的准备 就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微露了下脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触了吗？ 跟Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不关你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用自己的方式猎杀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就轮到你了 玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二同学昨天回去得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那个… 放学之后我去找早苗的时候你已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有追问你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 明明天气预报没说过会下雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得还真是有够轰动啊 加兰特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚参与袭击的人还是尽快出境比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不必担心 已经基本上全都出境了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 不留下任何与梧桐组有关的证据而抹杀掉徐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对此表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望 以后要在日本行动的话 请务必先通告一下计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不是什么高难度的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照计划行动的话 就不会有那么多人进棺材了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说「Phantom」没出现的时候 我就应该预料到事态会如此发展
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要太过自责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drei自身有缺陷那也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drei很急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的Drei还没有正式继承「Phantom」的名号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为她还没有与前任「Phantom」一决雌雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能名副其实地坐上「Phantom」之位的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drei也将会拥有与之相符的沉着与从容了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 只要她亲手打败Zwei的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二 今天没带便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没带 但是茂木你怎么知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起去食堂吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是没问题 但是你的便当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二节课之后吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天的功臣茂木 允许你坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那就失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得 是「不受欢迎的茂木」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是怎么介绍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 把我给卖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啦 分点幸福给我吧 一点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真迫切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这样也不错啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟江连一起用餐真是荣幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们果然很合得来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在人群之中 卡尔也不能轻易下手是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我留着位置 我去买饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要B套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 之前玲二说有急事原来是去找你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有些事 无论如何都想跟哥哥商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 我明知哥哥在跟美绪约会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是约会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是这么回事的话 你早说不就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 总觉得太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不懂少女心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种人就要处以「夹掉配菜刑」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有你满怀幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么幸福？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这呆头鹅还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上渴望得到幸福的人可是多如牛毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如茂木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 别人拜托我给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学弟学妹有事找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那小小的幸福飞走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你说的只要一点就好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去驱赶害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江连很受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都这么计较的话 你会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 毕竟是唯一的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次一定补偿你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的补偿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 你能够下手杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为命令 也不是因为被逼无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出于你自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的特点 Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受纯粹的杀意支撑着杀人行为的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与凭雕虫小技洗脑并加强心理暗示的Ein 有着天壤之别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说 你是个失败作品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你却为我的研究指明了新的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对「憎恨」这一主题也试着进行了创作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了吗 我引以为豪的第三作 Drei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对卡尔…做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就结论来说 我什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有洗脑 没有暗示 也全然没有干涉她的情绪和记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 彻底打磨擦亮了 她与生俱来的仇恨心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你给我留下这么个难得的人才 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞斯 只有你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可恨是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在你却杀不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的自制力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你同时兼备纯粹的憎恨和冷静的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出色的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点上Drei稍有不足 难以抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少还是懂得怎么来掩人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去援助她的话 就赶快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多该出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 没人会打搅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 应该叫你前任「Phantom」？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了猎杀那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了 这一个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
